# Interview Coach ships with no server-side secrets.
#
# The LLM API key lives in your browser, encrypted with a passphrase you
# choose on the Settings page (AES-256-GCM + PBKDF2-SHA256, 200k iterations).
# The Next.js server only proxies `/api/chat` requests to the provider; it
# never stores the key on disk.
#
# There is nothing required here for the app to run — this file exists
# primarily so deployment checks can verify a clean environment. Add any
# hosting-specific variables (analytics, error reporting, etc.) below.
